og.description: Methodist Jennie Edmundson Hospital has been awarded a $95,500 grant by the Iowa Affiliate of Susan G. Komen to provide breast cancer screening and education to women in Pottawattamie, Mills, Montgomery, Cass, Shelby and Adair counties.
